Program: Crossing Continents
Title: Escape from North Korea
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b012r7jv
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 1 Aug 2011
Lucy Williamson reports from Seoul on the dangerous trade of the people brokers, smuggling desperate people out of North Korea to the safety of the South. She investigates the way the South Korean government tries to integrate refugees from the North into their own modern, open society - and the challenges this creates for people who have only known poverty and extreme political repression. Show less